{"_id":"hei57epstq","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Limited Degree","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":-1}}}
{"_id":"uhlddhtulu","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Activation","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","notes":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":-1}}}
{"_id":"tcuepkmc857","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Instant Recovery","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":-1}}}
{"_id":"3pcej038az4","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Check Required","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":-1}}}
{"_id":"2xsxprfbvn5","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Concentration","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":-1}}}
